Package k23b.ac.fragments

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NavigationDrawerFragment.NavigationDrawerCallbacks
    Callbacks interface that all activities using this fragment must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgentsFragment
    The Fragment which attached to the Main Activity offers the list of available Agents
    FragmentBase
    Parent class for the Agents, Jobs, Login, Register, ResultsAgent, ResultsAll Fragments.
    JobsFragment
    The Fragment which attached to the Main Activity offers the list of available Jobs out of a list of Agents.
    LoginFragment
    The Fragment in which the action of Login is initiated or the RegisterActivity is started.
    NavigationDrawerFragment
    Fragment used for managing interactions for and presentation of a navigation drawer.
    RegisterFragment
    The Fragment in which the action of Registration is initiated.
    ResultsAgentFragment
    The Fragment which attached to the Main Activity offers the list of available Results of a single Agent out of a list of the latter.
    ResultsAllFragment
    The Fragment which attached to the Main Activity offers the list of all available Results.
    StartFragment
    The Fragment in which the necessary initialiasation for the services occur and the LoginActivity starts.
